subject: College Athletics
Football (College)
Traffic and Parking Violations
lead_paragraph: The N.C.A.A. is investigating whether Ohio State quarterback Terrelle Pryor’s cars violate its rules, while the state of Ohio says he should not be driving one because his driving privileges are suspended.
